<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Jared Henriques</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Builder, dad, optimist. Be a good human. Do good work. Make things better." />
		<style>
			@font-face {
				font-family: 'Reader';
				src: url('/fonts/reader-regular.woff2') format('woff2'),
					 url('/fonts/reader-regular.woff') format('woff');
				font-weight: normal;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			html {
				font-size: 18px;
			}

			body {
				font-family: 'Reader', Georgia, serif;
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: #2c2c2c;
				background: #f8f6f3;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 2rem;
			}

			main {
				max-width: 480px;
				width: 100%;
			}

			.bio {
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}

			.bio h1 {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				font-weight: normal;
				margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
			}

			.bio p {
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
				color: #3d3d3d;
			}

			.bio .tagline {
				font-style: italic;
				color: #6b6b6b;
				margin-top: 1.25rem;
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			.links {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 1.25rem;
			}

			.links a {
				color: #6b6b6b;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				transition: color 0.2s;
			}

			.links a:hover {
				color: #2c2c2c;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<section class="bio">
				<h1>Hey, I'm Jared Henriques.</h1>
				<p>I ran a branding studio, now I'm at Measure.</p>
				<p>Moved to Victoria, BC with my wife and two kids. Thinking about raising a family and building things in an era where everything's shifting.</p>
				<p class="tagline">Be a good human. Do good work. Make things better.</p>
			</section>

			<nav class="links">
				<a href="https://twitter.com/jaredhenriques" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
				<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jaredhenriques" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
				<a href="mailto:hello@jared.is">Email</a>
			</nav>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
